{"tid":660143,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[日韓合作]Produce 48 討論區：6月首播","createTime":"2018-05-10T12:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T20:53:26.000Z","uid":2832,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d49343d5ba917c9a84b89f90babbbac109233452","tid":660143,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"Mnet的《Produce 48》將在6月15日跟大家見面啦！ 主題曲《是我的（PICK ME）》也將在明晚首次公開~<br />\n<br />\n《Produce 48》作為Mnet《Produce 101》系列的第三季，由展現了優秀製作能力的日本女團AKB48與Mnet招牌偶像選拔節目相結合，形成超大型的女團選拔節目。<br />\n<br />\n國民製作人代表由李昇基擔任，樂團FTIsland主唱李洪基、女團SISTAR出身的昭宥負責指導演唱，Cheetah負責rap部分，編舞家裴允靜、崔英俊、MAY J LEE擔任編舞。<br />\n<br />\n節目已經在4月11日開始錄製，來自日韓的96位參賽者開始共同住宿；主題曲《是我的（PICK ME）》也已經錄製完畢，將在明晚的《M！ Countdown》裡首次與大家見面。<br />\n<br />\n究竟，《Produce 48》能否誕生出堪比第一季的I.O.I和第二季的Wanna One的偶像組合呢？ 讓我們拭目以待吧~~<br />\n<br />\n（圖源：Mnet，KSD韓星網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UOmolLOQ7Rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUOmolLOQ7Rs&d=m%2F6%2BbClpgv5GVoVxpEBIjZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fa823168\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UOmolLOQ7Rs</a>"},{"pid":"ba615cf636003847a616de40fcdc48ba342a9c24","tid":660143,"uid":17019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"今集好多日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec17f6bcc7347879124a787a6335e150e897945","tid":660143,"uid":17019,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/205547_75f266a01096c7c6df959ed0b8574b79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F205547_75f266a01096c7c6df959ed0b8574b79.png&h=4fb0da38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左邊呢個好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee70ad0b87b7dbf33075b4a62747b74ba1216d00","tid":660143,"uid":52536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quot